<br>
Your arguements are about as old and worn as they come.<br>
They are based on 2 simple points<br>
1) Clerics are more desirable to any group<br>
2) Druids can solo better.<br>
<br>
From these (2) Acceptable facts, you leap to the conclusion that Its acceptable.<br>
<br>
It is not.  First, if all I want to do as a Druid is Solo, I will go play my Playstation 2.  Do not tell me &quot;because you can solo, you don't need a group so its okay that you can be worthless to a group and spend hours and hours LFG.&quot;<br>
<br>
Thats a bunch of bull.<br>
<br>
Secondly, <br>
Craft your own damn petition for clerics.  God knows they need it.  Spells that are anti-planes/deity based, or undead upgrades, etc.<br>
<br>
All with focus, of making clerics better for soloing.<br>
<br>
Before you respond to the above.  Please explain to me why<br>
its acceptable that every high end guild has 2 things.<br>
((key word explain why its acceptable))<br>
1) Has 3* or more clerics than druids for a raid<br>
2) Gives Loot Rites on FT/High AC wis pieces to Clerics first, shamans second, druids third.<br>
<br>
You seem focus on a paper game.  You point out a select few high end items, that are cleric/druid usable.  Now, heres my test for you.  Find 10 Druids who have these items, while Clerics in thier guild have worse.   Try reverse.  Find 10 Clerics who have have these, while Druids in thier guild have worse. <br>
<br>
Again, you accuse druids not thinking big picture, yet you don't.  You take out CH sometimes.  You take out how top guilds structure loot.  You take out membership in top guilds.<br>
<br>
In another words, please explain WHY druids should be 2nd class citizens in any end guild?<br>
<br>
Also, why is it Clerics whine so much about Druids?  Shamans can solo better (than a druid, and especially a cleric).  Shamans can also replace a Cleric in many cases.  ((Notice though that this is mostly at 60 with torpor.  IE at the END of the game.))<br>
<br>
A 60 Shaman can easily replace a 50 to 54 Cleric.  <br>
A 60 Druid can not.<br>
<br>
A 60 Melee can replace a 50 to 54 Warrior.<br>
<br>
Nuff Said.<br>
